&reftitle.description;
public arrayGearmanClient::jobStatusByUniqueKey stringunique_key
Gets the status of a background job, identified by the unique key that was assigned to it when it was submitted. This is the counterpart of GearmanClient::jobStatus, which looks the job up by its job handle instead.

&reftitle.parameters;


  unique_key


    The unique key of the job to look up.
